{"id": "1445678679857434653", "channel_id": "1441445942787178517", "type": 0, "author_id": "944524613168279553", "author_name": "ena04564", "author_bot": false, "content": "玫瑰你可以開局掛零費光環後就不用理她了，光環是全局探索有效的", "timestamp": "2025-12-03T07:30:56.689000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1441445942787178517", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "一點塔薇玩家的小小心得", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179700470460447"]}
