{"id": "1445683681011437600", "channel_id": "1441445942787178517", "type": 0, "author_id": "727340747669635132", "author_name": "hon_ey0", "author_bot": false, "content": "有在考慮課淵海紀行那裡還有個萬能啟靈大不了先給小玫瑰<:410082304598343682:1139503282742636574>", "timestamp": "2025-12-03T07:50:49.057000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🛐", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1441445942787178517", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "一點塔薇玩家的小小心得", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179700470460447"]}
{"id": "1445696307019776101", "channel_id": "1441445942787178517", "type": 0, "author_id": "944524613168279553", "author_name": "ena04564", "author_bot": false, "content": "哇你溫有+7欸可以直接可以考慮跟融朵一起上\n~~左腳踩右腳實現狂氣自由~~\n道中刪牌可以考慮刪掉溫柯爾3費，命輪的部分溫柯爾可以帶神王跟牧羊人手杖（sr）\n開局有一個普通大會比較好操作一點\n\n不帶溫的話，也可以帶女僕，或者普通拉蒙娜", "timestamp": "2025-12-03T08:40:59.332000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1441445942787178517", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "一點塔薇玩家的小小心得", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179700470460447"]}
